 // .NET 8: doc is null
 // .NET 9: doc is not null, doc.RootElement.ValueKind == JsonValueKind.Null
 ```

 **Fix:** Update code that checks `doc is null` to also check `doc.RootElement.ValueKind`:
 ```csharp
